---
title: Smart Cheddar and Turkey Meatballs with Blueberry BBQ Sauce and Roasted Veggies
description: Sweet and smoky blueberry BBQ sauce is the star of this meal. It smothers cheddar-studded turkey meatballs in this 4-star dinner!

